{"tid":1970948,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【武漢肺炎】傳廣東網遊禁現殭屍、瘟疫 警告有玩家「宣揚分裂祖國」","createTime":"2020-04-13T14:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T15:43:46.000Z","uid":104138,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e6f0ea98383714ebed78a6eec59cf33d20094d26","tid":1970948,"uid":104138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:06:50.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情全球肆虐，不少人留在家中打機度日，早前熱爆的任天堂Switch遊戲《動物森友會》卻突然在內地淘寶下架，疑是因玩法太過自由，觸碰中共敏感神經。有內地網民發現，廣東當局上月曾發出一份關於遊戲監管的要求，規定不得在遊戲中出現殭屍、瘟疫等映射當前武漢肺炎等言論，亦不可以出現「死」、「鬼」、「妖」等不良字眼。文件又要求，遊戲不可以全球使用同一伺服器，疑是要將內地玩家分隔，免受境外資訊「荼毒」。<br />\n<br />\n內地自媒體《遊戲葡萄》昨日發表的一篇文章，聲稱取得一間出版社的3月文件，整理內地當局對遊戲監管的一系列要求。報道引述多名知情人士確認，該份文檔來自廣東，比照之前上海、北京等地區遊戲公司的會議紀要，內容多了不少細節。<br />\n<br />\n全文請去<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200413/KGDD2UBX4NKOOPCQUR5IYQRNOI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200413%2FKGDD2UBX4NKOOPCQUR5IYQRNOI%2F&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=1e2da4e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200413%2FKGDD2UBX4NKOOPCQUR5IYQRNOI%2F&h=fccff892\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200413/KGDD2UBX4NKOOPCQUR5IYQRNOI/</a><br />\n<br />\n改名叫魂。初弒就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa1d98bff30044462de7ecad9627074dffa95a9a","tid":1970948,"uid":72749,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:08:23.000Z","msg":"你媽*了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb1246fe7a564dfd12a2acf8fe951fdbfb1009c","tid":1970948,"uid":231583,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/NOCeOYy.gif\" />"},{"pid":"b8be42521b4e5416291c333d455365c80a949a3f","tid":1970948,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T14:10:12.000Z","msg":"Pus